npx lint-staged

# Budget guard: every level-2 section of REFERENCE.md must fit inside the
# MCP tool-output budget so agents can fetch it in one round via
# `klura://reference#<slug>`. Also verifies every fragment pointer in
# SKILL.md resolves to a real section. Runs on every commit (test is fast)
# rather than gating on file changes — reference drift is the exact class
# of regression that's easy to miss on a commit that "shouldn't" touch it.
npm run --silent check:reference
